data.description: What a CUTE Home! Top quality finish outs. This Trinity Classic Home will not disappoint. Very open floor plan, lots of storage, big pantry, nice size rooms and closets. 3 bedrooms downstairs and large bonus or 4th bedroom with full bathroom upstairs. Great for mother-in-law suite, office or 4th bedroom. Great location, minutes from the schools and easy access to 199.
